EU’s Rehn Says Illusory to See Orderly Greek Debt Restructuring

-- B y   M e e r a   L o u i s
-- 
2011-09-22T15:01:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/eu-s-rehn-says-illusory-to-see-orderly-greek-debt-restructuring.html
European Union Economic and
Monetary Affairs Commissioner  Olli Rehn  said today that it is
“illusory” to consider a neat and tidy way to restructure
Greek debt. “We are not seeing a Greek default as a plausible
scenario,” Rehn said at an event in  Washington .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Meera Louis in Washington at 
